@startuml SD14_View_Profile
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
title SD-14: View User Profile + Karma

actor "Viewer" as V
participant "Astro SSR" as FE
participant "Envoy\nGateway" as GW
participant "User\nService" as USER
database "pg-user" as DBUSER
database "Redis\n(db4)" as CACHE
participant "Post\nService" as POST
database "pg-post\n(sharded)" as DBPOST
participant "Comment\nService" as CMT
database "ScyllaDB" as SCYLLA

V -> FE : Navigate to u/someuser
FE -> GW : GET /api/users/someuser\n(no JWT required for public profile)

== Fetch Profile ==
GW -> USER : gRPC GetProfile("someuser")
USER -> CACHE : GET profile:someuser
alt Cache HIT
    CACHE --> USER : Cached profile
else Cache MISS
    USER -> DBUSER : SELECT username, karma,\ncake_day, avatar\nFROM users
    USER -> CACHE : SET profile:someuser\n(TTL: 10 min)
end
USER --> GW : Profile data

== Fetch User's Posts ==
GW -> POST : gRPC GetUserPosts(user_id, page)
POST -> DBPOST : SELECT posts\nWHERE author_id = user_id\nORDER BY created_at DESC\nLIMIT 25
POST --> GW : Post list

== Fetch User's Comments ==
GW -> CMT : gRPC GetUserComments(user_id, page)
CMT -> SCYLLA : Query comments by author\n(secondary index)
CMT --> GW : Comment list

GW --> FE : JSON {profile, posts, comments}
FE -> FE : Server-side render
FE --> V : Profile page\n(username, karma, cake_day,\nposts tab, comments tab)

note right of V
    Only username, karma,
    and cake_day are visible.
    Email and auth method
    are never exposed.
end note
@enduml
